                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>78 Nassan St</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>N.Y.</placeName>\n                <date>July 26/66</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Revd dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I have just<lb/> rec'd your Bibles. Didn't<lb/> fully understand the\n                price.<lb/> Was it $15 wholesale or retail?<lb/> And is the Bible in sheets $2.50\n                to<lb/> meâ€” it was for my own use</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I send the circular, which<lb/> has just been printed.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Saw <persName>Mr Peixotto</persName>. He will shortly<lb/> visit\n                    <placeName>Phila.</placeName> &amp; will speak with<lb/> you on the subject of\n                the<lb/> College. It would be well to<lb/> reserve opinion, until you<lb/> see\n                him.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33t9dp6f/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
