                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>My brother explained to you<lb/> I presume the reason<lb/> of my not calling in<lb/>\n                person <date>Monday</date> AM</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Truly Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\"><persName role=\"author\">M. J. Isaacs</persName>.</p>\n            <p>We want to issue shortly<lb/> blanks for statistics. Also<lb/> we should take some\n                action<lb/> as to Publications. If you<lb/> have any suggestions please<lb/>\n                communicate them.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
